WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:05.104
<i>It all started when a time travel
experiment I was conducting... </i>

00:05.171 --> 00:08.106
<i>went... a little caca. </i>

00:08.173 --> 00:11.666
<i>In the blink of a cosmic clock,
I went from quantum physicist</i>

00:11.745 --> 00:15.112
<i>to air force test pilot,</i>

00:15.181 --> 00:17.911
<i>which could have been
fun if I knew how to fly. </i>

00:17.984 --> 00:21.249
<i>Fortunately, I had help,
an observer from the project named Al. </i>

00:21.321 --> 00:25.348
<i>Unfortunately, Al's a hologram,
so all he can lend is moral support. </i>

00:25.425 --> 00:28.417
<i>Anyway, here I am,
bouncing around in time,</i>

00:28.495 --> 00:30.588
<i>putting things right
that once went wrong,</i>

00:30.663 --> 00:34.531
<i>a sort of time-traveling Lone Ranger
with Al as my Tonto,</i>

00:34.601 --> 00:37.126
<i>and I don't even need a mask. </i>

00:38.138 --> 00:40.072
Oh, boy.

